					<p>Very glad you enjoyed it :&gt;. It&#8217;s not as positive as all that, though; if you think through the implications, a &#8220;few dozen&#8221; staying behind are not going to be enough to start a brave new anything. I see them dying off in a generation or two &#8211; when I say &#8220;gone&#8221;, I really mean it. I&#8217;m nasty that way.</p>
