				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I see what you mean with &#8220;temperatures&#8221;. It actually works for me when I substitute another word: &#8220;now the skies are clear, the cats dropping&#8221; (totally different image, though 😛 ). Somehow &#8220;temperatures&#8221; still refuses to sound right to me, but that&#8217;s probably a personal foible on my part.</p>
